PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of Stuart E. Hendin, of Otawa, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of VIA Rail Canada Inc. to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Laura Sabia, whose term has expired.
